<div class="o-layout__item u-width-12 u-width-12--m" style="margin-top: 2rem;">	
	<h3 class="u-text-uppercase"><strong>What are your sale policies?</strong></h3>
	<p>Policies vary depending on the sale or promotion being conducted. Terms may include, but are not limited to: - Restrictions apply - Some brands excluded - Subject to change without notice - Offer valid for limited time only - Specials and discounts cannot be combined or used with other offers Contact us with questions about the terms of any sale or promotion.</p>
	<h3 class="u-text-uppercase"><strong>How often do you have sales?</strong></h3>
	<p>Sales are held at various times of the year. Sales can be site-wide, or for specific items.</p>
	<h3 class="u-text-uppercase"><strong>How can I find out about your sales?</strong></h3>
	<p>The best way to find out about our sales, or any of our specials and promotions is to join our mailing list. Just scroll down to the next section of this page.</p>	
</div>
